title: THE JAGGED WOMEN'S JEANS IN MIDNIGHT BLACK
description:

title: TIMELESS THREADS TOTE BAG
description:
Step into the world of the ‘Timeless Threads Totebag’ a fusion of style and soul.
With unique denim handles and our exclusive "Timeless Threads" logo proudly crafted on one side, this tote isn't just an accessory; it's a canvas of self-expression.

Flip it over, and you'll find the lyrics of our favorite song, a whisper of inspiration that accompanies you on every journey.

Designed to effortlessly accommodate your laptop, wallet, makeup and all your daily essentials.

Size: 50x45 cms.
